    "summary": "在成都与青城山之间切换，体验旅途中的冷热反差。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s1",
      "text": "At last, I arrived in Chengdu.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p1",
      "tr": "终于，我到达了成都。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主谓宾",
      "d": "'At last'表示终于，强调经过一段时间的等待。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/YWFknHy6StEPsXMMQfBC6P.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s2",
      "text": "My friend Haoyu took me to a restaurant right from the airport.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p1",
      "tr": "我的朋友浩宇直接从机场带我去了一家餐馆。",
      "g": "主谓宾补",
      "d": "'take sb to...'表示带某人去某地。'right from'表示直接从...。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/4ajq3J6GjRXv2TMJJMaLLg.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s3",
      "text": "I just couldn’t wait to try Sichuan hot pot!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p1",
      "tr": "我迫不及待地想尝尝四川火锅！",
      "g": "主谓宾",
      "d": "'couldn’t wait to do sth'表示迫不及待做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/hB9nUuwyaKGqnNJDjcAgBL.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s4",
      "text": "But the first taste made my mouth burn!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p2",
      "tr": "但是第一口就让我的嘴巴着火了！",
      "g": "使役动词结构",
      "d": "'make sb/sth do sth'使某人/某物做某事。这里指辣得嘴巴像烧起来一样。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UXR7DNFdoJ2fSg4TLfv8g4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s5",
      "text": "The food was much hotter than I expected.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p2",
      "tr": "食物比我预期的要辣得多。",
      "g": "比较级",
      "d": "'hotter than'表示比...更辣。'much'修饰比较级表示程度深。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/6MzEWRDB2zHFrPNKfTo252.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s6",
      "text": "I took a deep breath and drank a whole glass of iced lemon tea.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p2",
      "tr": "我深吸了一口气，喝了一整杯冰柠檬茶。",
      "g": "并列谓语",
      "d": "'took'和'drank'是并列的过去式动词。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/WQaV9Svd8xxuwxfERTsNS9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s7",
      "text": "“Do you want something less hot?” Haoyu said.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p3",
      "tr": "“你想吃点不那么辣的吗？”浩宇说。",
      "g": "一般疑问句",
      "d": "'something less hot'形容词修饰不定代词后置。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/nETWBmaYWUzEQ6jqgruDmV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s8",
      "text": "“No,” I replied.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p4",
      "tr": "“不，”我回答道。",
      "g": "直接引语",
      "d": "简单的回答。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/df5yQvdbkSLvuZz6VkeXWN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s9",
      "text": "“When in China, do as the Chinese do!”",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p4",
      "tr": "“入乡随俗！”",
      "g": "谚语",
      "d": "意为'在罗马就像罗马人一样做'，即入乡随俗。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/xvRsTUD68qcB9py72rgLQN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s10",
      "text": "I carefully took a small mouthful.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p4",
      "tr": "我小心翼翼地吃了一小口。",
      "g": "主谓宾",
      "d": "'carefully'修饰动词'took'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/WfqdHEGEmnh4LFygvL6Dff.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s11",
      "text": "Surprisingly, I started to enjoy the taste.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p4",
      "tr": "令人惊讶的是，我开始享受这种味道。",
      "g": "状语 + 主谓宾",
      "d": "'start to do sth'开始做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/KnoM9Tz9K5FUgzi5bXUB6n.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s12",
      "text": "And cooking hot pot was just as fun as eating it!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p4",
      "tr": "而且煮火锅和吃火锅一样有趣！",
      "g": "同级比较",
      "d": "'as...as'表示和...一样。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/n9BAChzyyGCnuNqfRHcnPB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s13",
      "text": "After lunch, things went from really hot to totally cool – we went to the new Sanxingdui Museum!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p5",
      "tr": "午饭后，我们从热辣的火锅店到了一个完全不同的凉爽且很酷的地方——我们去参观了三星堆博物馆新馆！",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主谓结构",
      "d": "'from...to...'从...到...。'cool'这里双关，指凉爽也指酷。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/bc2tfVbP3wgdbyboNypMA5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s14",
      "text": "The masks were fantastic.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p5",
      "tr": "面具太棒了。",
      "g": "主系表",
      "d": "'fantastic'形容词作表语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/rAHUgobCviGWUTUntCWAR4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s15",
      "text": "“Why are their eyes and ears much bigger than normal ones?",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p5",
      "tr": "“为什么他们的眼睛和耳朵比正常的要大得多？",
      "g": "特殊疑问句 + 比较级",
      "d": "'bigger than'比较级。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/iUgRqi4hMcWxGGaoyenmYb.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s16",
      "text": "Were ancient Shu people able to see and hear further than us?” I wondered.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p5",
      "tr": "古蜀人能比我们看和听得更远吗？”我想知道。",
      "g": "一般疑问句",
      "d": "'be able to'能够。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/afttpwQXo5oHEDRFD2kLiG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s17",
      "text": "I wanted to stay in the museum for a week!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p5",
      "tr": "我想在博物馆待一个星期！",
      "g": "主谓宾",
      "d": "'want to do sth'想要做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/jDJoizLqjcnMxGSuHaxqge.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s18",
      "text": "My first day in China was full of fun: I tried new food and went to an exciting place.",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p6",
      "tr": "我在中国的第一天充满了乐趣：我尝试了新食物，去了一个令人兴奋的地方。",
      "g": "主系表 + 解释说明",
      "d": "'be full of'充满。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/BtQQ6QUssuU56fR9z2T2FR.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u14-article-s19",
      "text": "I’m really looking forward to the rest of my trip around China!",
      "paragraphId": "u14-article-p6",
      "tr": "我真的很期待我在中国的余下旅程！",
      "g": "进行时态",
      "d": "'look forward to'期待，to是介词，后接名词。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/MHMgkSypyEgnjm2heBGw7d.mp3"
    }
  ],
